10 benefit extension
11 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to amend
12 Vermont’s Public Records Act and provisions of Title 32 to provide that
13 information concerning severance pay and benefit extension agreements shall
14 be available for public inspection and copying under Vermont’s Public
15 Records Act.
16 An act relating to access to information concerning benefit extension
17 agreements for employees of public agencies
