2 Sec. 1. 1 V.S.A. § 317 is amended to read:
3 § 317. DEFINITIONS; PUBLIC AGENCY; PUBLIC RECORDS AND
4 DOCUMENTS; EXEMPTIONS
5 * * *
6 (c) The following public records are exempt from public inspection and
7 copying:
8 * * *
9 (7) Personal documents relating to an individual, including information
10 in any files maintained to hire, evaluate, promote, or discipline any employee
11 of a public agency; information in any files relating to personal finances; or
12 medical or psychological facts concerning any individual or corporation;
13 provided, however, that all information in personnel files of an individual
14 employee of any public agency shall be made available to that individual
15 employee or his or her designated representative and information concerning
16 severance pay or the extension of employment benefits beyond the date of
